race.comment: PASS LINE (1) finished third two runs back at this track (Dirt) then improved last time out to score by half a length over 1609m at this track (Dirt). Ramon A Vazquez scored on him last time and retains the ride. Perfectly placed and is sure to give this a mighty shake. GO WEST (6) lines up on the back of a 7 length fifth over 1308m at Churchill Downs. Race sets up well for him. R D C POSSE (9) was in contention on the turn and finished third last start at the first run back from a spell over 1408m at this track (Dirt), beaten one length. Suitably placed so anticipating a big run again. KICK IT AGAIN BOB (7) showed good early speed then led into the straight last start before fighting on to finish second, beaten 0.8 lengths, over 1408m at this track (Dirt). Well-placed and can feature in the finish. Something for the Multiples: THREEFIFTYSEVEN (5)
